text: Hugo Peitsch (21 December 1878 - 10 September 1951) was a German gymnast. He competed at the 1900 Summer Olympics and the 1904 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1878 births Category:1951 deaths Category:German male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Germany Category:Gymnasts at the 1900 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1904 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts from Berlin
